
Creating a virtual enviroment:
python3 -m venv <name_of_virtualenv>

Installing 
To run python tests:
python -m unittest discover tests/unit_tests   


You need Geckodrive to run selenium tests , you can follow this on how to set up:
https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/how-to-install-selenium-in-python/

To run selenium tests:
python tests/web_tests/test_web_page.py
*please not the the text file path will need to be update with your file path


To run flask application :
python app.py

